      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s been such a reliable partner on the road. It\u2019s still in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride that still looks great in the driveway. I\u2019ve taken real pride in keeping it well-maintained, so it's ready to hit the road for its next big adventure with you! If you have any questions at all or just want to come take a look, please don't hesitate to reach out. I'd love to chat and find this car a great new home!",
