    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) that serves as a benchmark for high-revving, naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 3.2L inline-six engine remains the centerpiece, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized volumetric efficiency across the rev range. This example features a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is excellent, with the rear subframe reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. Suspension dynamics are enhanced by a set of Bilstein dampers, providing exceptional high-speed stability and communicative turn-in. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the internal mechanicals are primed for the 8,000 RPM redline. This is a mechanically sound, driver-oriented machine that balances raw feedback with sophisticated German kinematics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
